formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
Details of Annexure 3A of Form 3 has not been verified by us.  Same has ben provided on the basis of information provided by the promoter of the project.  Details of Form 3 has been provided on the basis of information of accounting data provided by the promoter.
-We have provided this certificate for cost incurred on the basis of data provided by promoter and explanation given by  promoter further we have not verified vouchers and transcations for expenses incurred by promoter
-As,compared to previous  Form-3 filed, it shows the major change in Cost Incurred and paid during the period.  However, as during previous issuance of Form-3 some of the Expenses has not been recorded by the promoter and shown as Loans and Advances in the books of accounts and due to the same, previous Form-3 shows lower expenses incurred and paid as compared to that actual.  However, as during the issuance of current Form-3, as promoter has recoreded expenses in books of accounts it shows the increase in current period thogh same was already incurred and paid in earlier period.
